---
import Welcome from '../components/Welcome.astro';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';

---

<Layout title='Welcome to Astro.'>
	<main class=' mx-auto m-2'>
		<div class=" hero min-h-screen">
			<div class="hero-overlay bg-stone-800 bg-opacity-80"></div>
			<div class="prose hero-content text-neutral-content text-center">
				<div class="max-w-screen">
        
                    <h1 class="mb-5 text-5xl font-bold">Our Services</h1>
                    
                    <div class="md:grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">

                        <div class="bg-stone-800 bg-opacity-20 shadow-lg p-4 rounded-lg">
                            <h2>
                                Hydro Jetting Services
                            </h2>
                            <p class="mb-5">
                                Our state-of-the-art hydro jetting technology provides a powerful and efficient solution for clearing even the most stubborn clogs. Using high-pressure water jets, we can safely remove blockages, including tough root intrusions, without causing damage to your pipes. This method not only clears the immediate problem but also thoroughly cleans the interior of your pipes, preventing future issues and ensuring optimal flow. Trust our experienced technicians to restore your plumbing system to peak performance with our reliable hydro jetting services.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    
                        <div class="bg-stone-800 bg-opacity-20 shadow-lg p-4 rounded-lg">
                            <h2>
                                Water Heater Replacement
                            </h2>
                            <p class="mb-5">
                                From electric to tankless to traditional tank heaters, weâ€™ve got your water heater needs covered. Our expert technicians can help you choose the right water heater for your home, ensuring energy efficiency and optimal performance. We handle everything from removal of your old unit to installation and testing of your new water heater, providing you with hot water when you need it most. Whether you're upgrading to a more efficient model or replacing a broken unit, trust us to deliver top-notch service and quality products.
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-stone-800 bg-opacity-20 shadow-lg p-4 rounded-lg">
                            <h2>Sewer Lateral Replacement</h2>
                            <p class="mb-5">
                                Many homes in San Francisco were originally constructed with terra cotta sewer systems, which can deteriorate and become compromised over time. Our expert team specializes in sewer lateral replacement, offering the most advanced and durable solutions to upgrade your sewer system. We use modern materials and techniques to ensure a long-lasting and reliable sewer line, minimizing the risk of future issues. Whether you're experiencing frequent backups, slow drains, or other sewer-related problems, trust us to provide a comprehensive assessment and a seamless replacement process that restores your home's plumbing integrity.
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-stone-800 bg-opacity-20 shadow-lg p-4 rounded-lg">
                            <h2>Toilet Services</h2>
                            <p class="mb-5">
                                From stubborn clogs to complete toilet rebuilds or replacements, our skilled technicians can handle it all. We use advanced tools and techniques to ensure your toilet is functioning efficiently and reliably. Whether it's a simple repair or a full installation, trust us to provide prompt and professional service to keep your bathroom in top condition.
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-stone-800 bg-opacity-20 shadow-lg p-4 rounded-lg">
                            <h2>Drain Clogs</h2>
                            <p class="mb-5">
                                Our comprehensive drain cleaning services cover your entire drain system, both inside and outside your home. We use state-of-the-art equipment to effectively clear blockages and ensure your pipes are flowing smoothly. Regular maintenance and prompt attention to clogs can prevent more serious plumbing issues down the line. Let us help you maintain a healthy and efficient drainage system.
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-stone-800 bg-opacity-20 shadow-lg p-4 rounded-lg">
                            <h2>Gas Systems</h2>
                            <p class="mb-5">
                                We offer the latest technologies in gas system installations and repairs, including MegaPress fittings and earthquake shutoff valves. Our experienced technicians ensure your gas lines are safe, efficient, and up to code. Whether you need a new installation, routine maintenance, or emergency repairs, we provide reliable and professional gas system services to keep your home safe and functional.
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-stone-800 bg-opacity-20 shadow-lg p-4 rounded-lg">
                            <h2>Re-piping</h2>
                            <p class="mb-5">
                                If your home's plumbing system is outdated or experiencing frequent issues, it may be time for a complete re-piping. We specialize in replacing entire water delivery systems with high-quality materials tailored to your specific needs. Our re-piping services ensure improved water pressure, better water quality, and a more reliable plumbing system. Trust our experts to deliver a seamless and efficient re-piping solution.
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-stone-800 bg-opacity-20 shadow-lg p-4 rounded-lg">
                            <h2>Sump Pumps</h2>
                            <p class="mb-5">
                                Protect your home from flooding and water damage with our sump pump services. We offer installation, replacement, and maintenance of sump pump systems to keep your basement or crawl space dry. Our technicians are skilled in selecting and installing the right sump pump for your home, ensuring reliable performance during heavy rains and water emergencies. Keep your home safe and dry with our expert sump pump services.
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-stone-800 bg-opacity-20 shadow-lg p-4 rounded-lg">
                            <h2>Comprehensive Plumbing Solutions</h2>
                            <p class="mb-5">
                                We offer a wide range of plumbing services to meet all your needs, from minor repairs to major installations. Our team is equipped to handle garbage disposal repairs, shower valve replacements, faucet installations, leak detection, and much more. No job is too big or too small for our skilled technicians. We pride ourselves on delivering prompt, reliable, and high-quality service to ensure your complete satisfaction. Contact us today for a free estimate and let us take care of all your plumbing needs with professionalism and expertise.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>  
        </div>
    </div>
	</main>
  </Layout>


<style>
	.hero {
		background-image: url('../assets/cover4.JPG');
	}

    .hero-content {
        max-width: 60%;
    }

    .h2 {
        color: black;
    }
</style>